0business%20in%20December.%20I%20sell%20the%20cookies%20by%20the%20half%20dozen%2C%20with%20five%20core%20flavors%20and%20one%20rotating%20seasonal%20taste.%20A%20regular%20box%20of%20six%20costs%20%2427%2C%20and%20I%20sell%20about%203%2C000%20cookies%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20cookies%20have%20fun%20names%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BSnarky%20Snickerdoodle%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BChocolate%20Fuckin'%20Chip%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BOatmeal%20Raisin'%20Hell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb12ea3b-5bd5-4db3-b5cb-63e8757e595f%5C%22%3EExpensive%20eggs%20and%20chocolate%20have%20hit%20me%20hard%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20blow%20to%20my%20business%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fegg-prices-expensive-avian-bird-flu-changing-tastes-cage-free-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoaring%20egg%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feaster-chocolate-expensive-price-of-cocoa-bitcoin-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echocolate%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20December%2C%20the%20eggs%20I%20bought%20were%20less%20than%20%24100%20for%20a%20case%20of%20180%2C%20but%20in%20mid-February%2C%20they%20were%20%24145%20for%20that%20same%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20chocolate%20prices%20rise%2060%25%20since%20December.%20That%20means%20the%20price%20of%20my%20ingredients%20skyrocketed%2C%20too.%20Ingredient%20costs%20went%20from%2018.5%25%20of%20my%20total%20costs%20to%20about%2023%25%20in%20February%2C%20which%20is%20huge%20for%20a%20small%20business%20like%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20tariffs%20have%20made%20everything%20feel%20like%20it's%20in%20free%20fall.%20And%20there's%20a%20100%25%20chance%20I%20will%20be%20affected%20by%20his%20tariffs%20on%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20source%20my%20cookie%20bags%20from%20a%20company%20called%20Pouch.me%2C%20which%20is%20based%20in%20Shanghai.%20I%20love%20them%20because%20they're%20so%20well%20customized%20and%20