.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What%20Ambedkar's%20Raised%20Finger%20Is%20Really%20Trying%20To%20Tell%20You%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmbedkar's%20raised%20finger%20pointed%20to%20an%20imminent%20state%20of%20bliss.%20It%20was%20just%20a%20few%20miles%20ahead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmbedkar%20was%20a%20national%20hero%20once%2C%20but%20these%20statues%20have%20reduced%20him%20to%20just%20a%20god%20of%20Dalits.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20competing%20environment%20of%20statues%20of%20gods%20big%20and%20small%2C%20a%20poorly%20designed%20statue%20of%20Dr%20Bhim%20Rao%20Ambedkar%20dressed%20in%20a%20gauche%20blue%20suit%20would%20often%20elicit%20this%20response%20each%20time%20we%20crossed%20it%20on%20our%20way%20to%20Agra.%20The%20statue%20meant%20that%20we%20were%20nearing%20the%20city%20where%20we%20would%20get%20access%20to%20ice%20cream%2C%20pineapple%20pastry%2C%20and%20a%20meal%20at%20our%20favourite%20restaurant.%20If%20my%20parents%20were%20feeling%20generous%20and%20had%20the%20cash%2C%20we%20could%20also%20get%20a%20toy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-year-old%20me%20had%20always%20associated%20the%20'Blue%20Statue'%20with%20happiness%20and%20gratification%20till%20it%20got%20corrupted%20by%20the%20caste%20acrimony%20that%20any%20child%20raised%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bupper%20caste%26quot%3B%20household%20is%20exposed%20to%20in%20the%20mofussil%20India%2C%20even%20if%20the%20immediate%20family%20is%20relatively%20progressive.%20One%20heard%20caste%20slurs%20on%20the%20streets%20being%20casually%20thrown%20around.%20Women%20in%20the%20household%20won't%20eat%20in%20the%20expensive%20chinaware%20because%20those%20plates%20were%20also%20laid%20out%20while%20entertaining%20friends%20who%20couldn't%20be%20fed%20in%20the%20home%20utensils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Those%20People'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20VP%20Singh%20implemented%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission.%20All%20and%20sundry%20instructed%20one%20to%20study%20harder%20than%20anyone%20else%20because%20now%20'those%20people'%20were%20getting%20all%20the%20benefits%2C%20thanks%20to%20reservations.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20no%20hope.%20These%20people%20are%20going%20to%20be%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20I%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20boarding%20school%20where%20casteism%20was%20all%20alive%20but%2C%20fortunately%2C%20institutionally%20suppressed.%20But%20there%20were%20stories%20that%20the%20upper%20caste%20kids%20often%20told%20each%20other.%20Like%20the%20one%20about%20how%20one%20Raja%20Bachchu%20Singh%20killed%20that%20insolent%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20in%20the%20parliament.%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20allegedly%20dared%20to%20insult%20a%20Rajput%20maharaja%20and%20was%20suitably%20punished.%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20need%20to%20know%20their%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20there%20was%20the%20political%20bile%20against%20Mayawati%20and%20Kanshiram%20propping%20up%20Ambedkar%20statues%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Even%20the%20not-so-casteist%20friends%20and%20family%20members%20showed%20their%20disapproval%20at%20this%20in-your-face%20assertion%20of%20identity.%20As%20if%20there%20was%20no%20other%20identity%20that%20had%20been%20asserted%20in%20an%20equally%20in-your-face%20manner.%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20minds%20after%20getting%20to%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'These%20People'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20there%20was%20an%20outrage%20during%20a%20family%20reunion%20when%20a%20cousin%20shared%20that%20she%20was%20excluded%20from%20any%20get-together%20that%20one%20of%20her%20professors%20hosted%20at%20home%20because%20he%20confused%20her%20with%20those%20people.%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20tell%20him%20how%20dare%20he!%20Just%20because%20these%20people%20have%20started%20using%20our%20surname%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20we%20have%20become%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20my%20brother%20would%20be%20routinely%20told%20by%20some%20of%20our%20father's%20friends%20that%20he%20was%20not%20supposed%20to%20touch%20the%20feet%20of%20a%20particular%20'uncle'.%20That%20particular%20uncle%20also%20squirmed%20when%20my%20brother%20did%20so.%20My%20father%20would%20also%20be%20lectured%20by%20some%20against%20hobnobbing%20with%20those%20people.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20brought%20these%20people%20to%20your%20head%2C%20and%20now%20they%20have%20lost%20theirs!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20my%20brother%20started%20hiding%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20visited%20his%20best%20friend's%20home%20and%20ate%20there%20every%20day.%20A%20neighbour%20found%20out%20and%20slapped%20him.%20%26quot%3BYour%20mother%20doesn't%20feed%20you%20enough%20that%20you%20have%20to%20eat%20with%20these%20people.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20there%20was%20a%20classmate%20at%20the%20university%20whom%20I%20was%20helping%20remember%20the%20names%20Mahad%20and%20Chavdar%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20our%20'Modern%20Indian%20Literature'%20final%20exam.%20He%20kept%20mixing%20them%20up.%20None%20of%20us%20had%20heard%20of%20the%20names%20of%20these%20places%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20poignant%20they%20were%20in%20reshaping%20the%20country's%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20I%20got%20married%20to%20a%20man%20whose%20simple%20family%20prepared%20for%20eternal%20penance%20for%20daring%20to%20make%20a%20Brahmin%20girl%20wash%20their%20utensils.%20However%2C%20they%20also%20believed%20in%20keeping%20a%20separate%20set%20of%20utensils%20for%20those%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20household.%20%26quot%3BWhite%20teacups%20for%20these%20people.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELike%20Poisoned%20Air%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECasteism%20was%20like%20poisoned%20air%20for%20both%20ends%20of%20the%20social%20spectrum.%20One%20didn't%20pay%20much%20attention%20to%20it%20till%20it%20killed%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20something%20happened.%20The%20poison%20became%20unbearable%2C%20and%20one%20began%20to%20gag.%20One's%20progressivism%20stuck%20out%20as%20fraudulent.%20Why%20were%20these%20people%20invisible%20despite%20the%20draconian%20reservation%20that%20allegedly%20robbed%20us%20of%20our%20due%20station%20in%20life%3F%20Why%20were%20particular%20surnames%20seen%20only%20in%20some%20political%20parties%20and%20not%20at%20our%20farewell%20parties%20or%20university%20get-together%20parties%3F%20Why%20were%20some%20people%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20sniff%20these%20people%20out%20and%20bludgeon%20them%20in%20the%20open%20streets%20to%20celebrate%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20lost%20elections%20and%20Mayawati%20never%20returned%20to%20power%20in%20UP%3F%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20can%20be%20identified%20from%20miles%20away%20due%20to%20their%20body%20odour.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20made%20perfect%20sense.%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20%3Cem%3EAnnihilation%20of%20Caste%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0became%20more%20than%20a%20book.%20It%20inspired%20personal%20gestures%20and%20social%20activism%20in%20those%20self-congratulatory%20years%20of%20the%20late%20teens%20and%20the%20early%20twenties.%20But%20it%20also%20became%20a%20utopia%20that%20frustrated%20more%20than%20it%20reassured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeaching%20at%20one%20of%20the%20best%20undergraduate%20colleges%20in%20Asia%2C%20a%20progressive%20haven%2C%20one%20still%20had%20to%20field%20students'%20acrimonious%20questions%20about%20the%20validity%20of%20any%20affirmative%20action.%20The%20staff%20room%20was%20still%20often%20filled%20with%20disdain%20for%20those%20who%20were%20loud%20in%20their%20declaration%20of%20anti-caste%20credentials.%20The%20imagined%20wounds%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20were%20still%20oozing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20still%20oozing%20even%20when%20these%20people%20who%20undeservedly%20got%20everything%20that%20we%20were%20denied%20are%20rarely%20seen%20in%20decision-making%20places%20in%20newsrooms%2C%20educational%20institutions%2C%20political%20offices%2C%20think%20tanks%2C%20and%20industry%20chambers.%20And%20those%20who%20are%20occasionally%20seen%20there%20have%20to%20justify%20their%20being.%20One%20day%2C%20perhaps%2C%20they%20won't%20feel%20the%20need%20to.%20Because%20one%20man%20pointed%20the%20country%20in%20a%20direction%20from%20which%20it%20can%20not%20be%20turned%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar's%20raised%20finger%2C%20though%20routinely%20vandalised%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20keeps%20the%20hope%20alive%20against%20all%20hopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744605540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fbr-ambedkar-dalit-rights_650x400_61514721809.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-ambedkars-raised-finger-is-really-telling-us-8159162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ambedkar's%20raised%20finger%2C%20though%20routinely%20vandalised%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20keeps%20the%20hope%20alive%20against%20all%20hopes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-ambedkars-raised-finger-is-really-telling-us-8159162%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BImportant%20Thing%20Is...%26quot%3B%3A%20PNB%20Scam%20Whistlblower%20On%20Mehul%20Choksi's%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPunjab%20National%20Bank%20Scam%20whistle-blower%20Hariprasad%20SV%20has%20hailed%20the%20arrest%20of%20fugitive%20Indian%20businessman%20Mehul%20Choksi%20by%20Belgium's%20Law%20Enforcement%20authorities%2C%20acting%20on%20the%20request%20of%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20Hariprasad%20termed%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20news%26quot%3B%20not%20only%20for%20India%20but%20for%20all%20those%20who%20were%20cheated%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWow%2C%20Mehul%20Choksi%20getting%20arrested%20in%20Belgium%20is%20great%20news%20not%20only%20for%20India%20but%20also%20for%20all%20those%20who%20got%20cheated%20by%20him.%20The%20government%20must%20bring%20him%20back%20to%20India%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20justice%20must%20be%20delivered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20bringing%20him%20back%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20to%20get%20back%20all%20those%20billions%20of%20dollars%20he%20looted%20from%20India%20and%20stashed%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%20Hopefully%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20will%20succeed%20this%20time.%20Great%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20Hariprasad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2026%2C%202016%2C%20Bengaluru-based%20entrepreneur%20Hari%20Prasad%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20(PMO)%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20a%20potential%20large-scale%20scam.%20In%20his%20communication%2C%20Prasad%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20balance%20sheets%20contained%20clear%20indicators%20that%20something%20was%20amiss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20sources%20say%20Choksi%20was%20arrested%20in%20Belgium%20on%20Saturday%20after%20local%20authorities%20confirmed%20his%20presence%20in%20the%20country.%20Sources%20further%20stated%20that%20preparations%20were%20being%20made%20for%20his%20extradition%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Choksi%20is%20currently%20preparing%20for%20a%20legal%20battle.%20His%20defence%20team%20plans%20to%20move%20for%20bail%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20will%20oppose%20his%20extradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20team%20states%20that%20Choksi%20has%20strong%20reasons%20to%20challenge%20the%20extradition%20request%2C%20citing%20his%20health%20condition%2C%20among%20other%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2065-year-old%20fugitive%20diamond%20merchant%20who%20left%20India%20on%20January%202%2C%202018%2C%20is%20wanted%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20for%20allegedly%20defrauding%20the%20PNB%20of%20Rs%2013%2C850%20crore.%20His%20nephew%2C%20Nirav%20Modi%2C%20was%20also%20involved%20with%20him%20in%20the%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20fled%20India%2C%20initially%20travelling%20to%20the%20United%20States%20before%20settling%20in%20Antigua.%20Before%20leaving%20India%2C%20Choksi%20took%20the%20citizenship%20of%20Antigua%20in%202017%20and%20was%20later%20arrested%20in%20Dominica%2C%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20flee%20to%20Cuba%2C%20although%20his%20counsel%20had%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20been%20kidnapped%20from%20Antigua.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDominica%20deported%20him%20back%20to%20Antigua%20despite%20India%20making%20a%20representation%20for%20extradition%20in%20the%20court.%20He%20left%20Dominica%2C%20reportedly%20to%20seek%20treatment%20for%20Cancer%20in%20Belgium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoksi%20allegedly%20connived%20with%20his%20associates%20and%20other%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20(PNB)%20officials%20from%202014%20to%202017%20and%20fraudulently%20obtained%20Letters%20of%20Undertaking%20and%20Foreign%20Letters%20of%20Credit%20from%20PNB%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20wrongful%20loss%20of%20Rs.%206097.63%20crore%20to%20PNB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744605420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F36j7jfho_mehul-choksi-hariprasad-sv-_625x300_14_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpnb-scam-whistle-blo