nt-noboa-and-his-plans-to-fight-crime%2Farticleshow%2F120269846.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhat-to-know-about-ecuadors-reelected-president-noboa-and-his-plans-to-fight-crime%2Famp_articleshow%2F120269846.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhat-to-know-about-ecuadors-reelected-president-noboa-and-his-plans-to-fight-crime%2Famp_articleshow%2F120269846.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mehul%20Choksi%20Kept%20Slipping%20Through%20Net.%20How%20Indian%20Agencies%20Pursued%20Him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDiamantaire%20Mehul%20Choksi's%20arrest%20in%20Belgium%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20relentless%20pursuit%20by%20Indian%20agencies%20for%20over%20seven%20years%20and%20spanning%20three%20countries%20that%20faced%20multiple%20setbacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gitanjali%20Group%20owner%20is%20accused%20of%20a%20Rs%2012%2C636%20crore%20fraud%20at%20the%20state-run%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20along%20with%20his%20nephew%20Nirav%20Modi%2C%20his%20wife%20Ami%20Modi%2C%20and%20his%20brother%20Neeshal%20Modi.%20Sixty-five-year-old%20Choksi%20fled%20India%20in%202018%2C%20shortly%20before%20the%20massive%20fraud%20came%20to%20light.%20He%20flew%20to%20Antigua%2C%20where%20he%20had%20taken%20citizenship%20through%20the%20investment%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Choksi%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%20for%20illegal%20entry.%20A%20CBI%20team%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20Caribbean%20nation%20to%20secure%20his%20custody.%20Choksi's%20lawyers%20told%20a%20Dominican%20court%20that%20he%20needed%20to%20return%20to%20Antigua%20for%20treatment%20and%20assured%20that%20he%20would%20return%20to%20face%20trial%20later.%20After%2051%20days%20in%20jail%2C%20Choksi%20got%20relief%20from%20the%20British%20Queen's%20Privy%20Council%20and%20the%20extradition%20could%20not%20proceed.%20He%20flew%20back%20to%20Antigua.%20Later%2C%20the%20illegal%20entry%20charges%20against%20him%20in%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%20were%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20tracked%20him%20throughout%20this%20time.%20Last%20year%2C%20they%20learned%20that%20he%20was%20in%20Belgium%2C%20and%20they%20promptly%20alerted%20the%20agencies%20there%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20agencies%20said.%20All%20documents%20regarding%20the%20fraud%20case%20were%20also%20shared.%20Belgian%20police%20arrested%20Choksi%20on%20April%2012%20and%20found%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20flee%20to%20Switzerland.%20Choksi's%20wife%20Preeti%20is%20a%20Belgian%20citizen.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20Choksi%20submitted%20fabricated%20documents%20to%20get%20a%20residency%20card%20in%20Belgium.%20He%20also%20concealed%20that%20he%20was%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%20and%20Antigua.%20Earlier%2C%20in%20February%2C%20Choksi's%20lawyer%20told%20a%20Mumbai%20court%20that%20he%20cannot%20return%20to%20India%20because%20he%20was%20in%20Belgium%20for%20blood%20cancer%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20businessman%20also%20said%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20cooperate%20with%20Indian%20agencies%20and%20appear%20before%20courts%20through%20video-conferencing%2C%20but%20this%20suggestion%20was%20rejected%20and%20the%20agencies%20kept%20working%20towards%20his%20extradition.%20These%20efforts%20have%20now%20culminated%20in%20his%20arrest%20and%20Indian%20authorities%20are%20now%20working%20to%20bring%20him%20back%20for%20trial.%20Choksi's%20legal%20team%20has%20said%20it%20will%20file%20for%20bail%20and%20oppose%20his%20extradition%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744605180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fjnbd9d3_mehul-choksi_625x300_14_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmehul-choksi-arrested-in-belgium-pnb-fraud-case-3-countries-7-years-indian-agencies-relentless-pursuit-of-mehul-choks