Those%20who%20burnt%20down%20police%20stations%20and%20beat%20cops%20to%20death%20are%20not%20being%20charged.%20Cases%20are%20being%20filed%20against%20Awami%20League%20leaders.%20Our%20leaders%20are%20not%20able%20to%20stay%20at%20home%2C%20everything%20has%20been%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus%20was%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20fallout%20but%20he%20is%20driven%20by%20his%20hunger%20for%20power%2C%20said%20Ms%20Hasina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20will%20this%20country%20run%20if%20the%20law%20enforcement%20personnel%20are%20being%20murdered%20in%20public%3F%20Doesn't%20Yunus%20understand%20this%3F%20Or%20is%20he%20guiding%20the%20country%20to%20doomsday%3F%20This%20fascist%20terrorist%20Yunus%20is%20destroying%20our%20country%20out%20of%20hunger%20for%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20Awami%20League%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BMurders%20Were%20Part%20Of%20Conspiracy%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbu%20Sayeed%20was%20a%20student%20activist%20who%20died%20during%20the%20massive%20quota%20agitation%20ahead%20of%20Ms%20Hasina's%20ouster.%20The%20police%20and%20the%20protesters%20made%20conflicting%20claims%20over%20the%20cause%20of%20his%20death%20at%20a%20clash%20in%20July%20last%20year.%20A%20more%20aggressive%20campaign%20by%20the%20students%20followed%20and%20Sayeed%20became%20the%20face%20of%20their%20protest.%20And%20as%20Bangladesh%20got%20an%20interim%20government%2C%20he%20was%20epitomised%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhero%20of%20the%20generation%26quot%3B%20and%20branded%20as%20a%20victim%20of%20Hasina's%20ruthlessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20a%20fact-finding%20report%20by%20the%20UN%20said%20Sayeed%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20extrajudicial%20killing%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20police.%20It%20also%20flagged%20the%20use%20of%207.62%20mm%20bullets%20by%20the%20police%20in%20some%20instances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%2C%20however%2C%20asserted%20the%20police%20used%20only%20rubber%20pellets%2C%20not%20metal%20bullets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-vows-to-return-to-bangladesh-to-bring-mobster-muhammad-yunus-to-justice-7742966%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20Vows%20To%20Return%20To%20Bangladesh%2C%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20Responds%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbu%20Sayeed%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20rubber%20bullet.%20The%20police%20didn't%20use%20metal%20bullets.%20A%20rock%20smashed%20his%20head%20when%20they%20were%20throwing%20stones%20at%20the%20police.%20Even%20the%20police%20had%20the%20right%20to%20defend%20themselves%20when%20attacked.%20But%20where%20did%20the%207.62%20mm%20bullet%20come%20from%3F%20Who%20brought%20that%20rifle%20to%20the%20protest%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20the%20former%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%20claimed%20a%20top%20official%20tried%20to%20uncover%20the%20truth%2C%20but%20he%20was%20shunted.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20an%20official%20identified%20the%20bullet%20and%20said%20he%20would%20find%20out%20which%20civilians%20had%20this%20type%20of%20gun%2C%20Yunus%20removed%20him%20from%20his%20post.%20He%20did%20so%20because%20he%20is%20responsible%20for%20this%20murder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20formed%20a%20judicial%20enquiry%20committee%20in%20July%20to%20probe%20the%20death%20of%20protesters%20but%20Yunus%20didn't%20let%20them%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20exhume%20Sayeed's%20body%20and%20conduct%20a%20forensic%20examination.%20It%20will%20be%20proved%20that%20all%20the%20murders%20were%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy.%20I%20didn't%20kill%20them%2C%20neither%20did%20Awami%20League%20nor%20the%20police.%20The%20police%20rather%20were%20victims.%20Those%20who%20unleashed%20violence%20were%20given%20indemnity.%20Will%20they%20be%20brought%20to%20justice%3F%20No%2C%20because%20Yunus%20engineered%20this.%20It%20was%20part%20of%20his