tening%20to%20choke%20off%20supplies%20to%20the%20West%20of%20components%20central%20to%20weapons%2C%20electronics%2C%20automakers%2C%20aerospace%20manufacturers%2C%20semiconductor%20companies%20and%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20consumer%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20government%20is%20drafting%20a%20new%20regulatory%20system%20for%20exports%2C%20and%20while%20the%20policies%20are%20being%20framed%2C%20the%20shipments%20of%20the%20magnets%2C%20essential%20for%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20almost%20everything%20ranging%20from%20cars%20to%20missiles%2C%20have%20been%20halted%20at%20many%20Chinese%20ports%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20report%2C%20once%20the%20new%20regulatory%20system%20is%20in%20place%2C%20it%20could%20permanently%20prevent%20supplies%20from%20reaching%20certain%20companies%2C%20including%20American%20military%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20Dependency%20On%20Chinese%20Imports%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20crackdown%20on%20exports%20is%20part%20of%20Beijing's%20retaliation%20against%20US%20President%20Trump's%20punishing%20trade%20war.%20China%20produces%20around%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20world's%20rare%20earths%2C%20a%20group%20of%2017%20elements%20used%20across%20the%20defense%2C%20electric%20vehicle%2C%20energy%20and%20electronics%20industries.%20Seven%20categories%20of%20medium%20and%20heavy%20rare%20earths%2C%20including%20samarium%2C%20gadolinium%2C%20terbium%2C%20dysprosium%2C%20lutetium%2C%20scandium%20and%20yttrium-related%20items%2C%20have%20been%20placed%20on%20the%20export%20control%20list.%20The%20United%20States%20has%20only%20one%20rare%20earths%20mine%2C%20and%20most%20of%20its%20supply%20comes%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20placed%20export%20restrictions%20on%20rare%20earth%20elements%20on%20April%202%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20package%20of%20tariffs%20and%20company%20restrictions%20in%20retaliation%20for%20Trump's%20decision%20to%20hike%20tariffs%20against%20most%20Chinese%20products%20to%2054%20per%20cent.%20The%20export%20curbs%20include%20not%20only%20mined%20minerals%20but%20permanent%20magnets%20and%20other%20finished%20products%20that%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20replace%2C%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20which%20Beijing%20had%20long%20hinted%20was%20possible%2C%20further%20ratchets%20up%20trade%20tensions%20between%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20economies%20and%20leaves%20American%20manufacturers%20scrambling%20for%20fresh%20supplies%20of%20the%20critical%20minerals%20they%20have%20relied%20upon%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20metals%20and%20special%20magnets%20made%20with%20them%20can%20only%20be%20shipped%20out%20of%20China%20with%20special%20export%20licenses%2C%20the%20NYT%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Beijing's%20system%20to%20issue%20these%20licenses%20is%20barely%20in%20place%2C%20which%20is%20causing%20consternation%20among%20industry%20executives%20that%20the%20process%20could%20drag%20on%20and%20that%20current%20supplies%20of%20minerals%20and%20products%20outside%20of%20China%20could%20run%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Move%20To%20Exert%20Dominance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20which%20affects%20exports%20to%20all%20countries%2C%20not%20just%20the%20US%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20demonstration%20of%20China's%20ability%20to%20weaponize%20its%20dominance%20over%20the%20mining%20and%20processing%20of%20the%20critical%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20export%20controls%20stop%20short%20of%20an%20outright%20ban%2C%20Beijing%20can%20throttle%20shipments%20by%20restricting%20the%20number%20of%20export%20licenses%20it%20issues.%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20Tesla%20and%20Apple%20are%20among%20the%20US%20companies%20that%20use%20Chinese%20rare%20earths%20in%20their%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20has%20stockpiles%20of%20some%20rare%20earths%2C%20but%20not%20enough%20to%20supply%20its%20defense%20contractors%20in%20perpetuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20already%20imposed%20outright%20bans%20on%20the%20export%20of%20three%20metals%20to%20the%20US%20and%20slapped%20export%20controls%20on%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20moves%20to%20restrict%20heavy%20rare%20earths%20are%20especially%20important%20because%20China%20has%20even%20tighter%20control%20over%20these%20elements%2C%20David%20Merriman%20at%20consultancy%20Project%20Blue%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20currently%20only%20one%20HREE%20(heavy%20rare%20earth%20element)%20focused%20operation%20outside%20of%20China%2C%20Myanmar%20and%20Laos%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20China%20has%20close%20involvement%20in%20supply%20chains%20from%20Myanmar%20and%20Laos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Rare%20Metals%20Are%20Important%20For%20The%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heavy%20rare%20earth%20metals%20put%20under%20export%20suspension%20by%20China%20are%20used%20in%20magnets--%20essential%20for%20many%20kinds%20of%20electric%20motors%20used%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20electric%20cars%2C%20drones%2C%20robots%2C%20missiles%20and%20spacecraft%20and%20gasoline-powered%20cars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20metals%20are%20required%20for%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20jet%20engines%2C%20lasers%2C%20car%20headlights%20and%20certain%20spark%20plugs%20and%20capacitors%2C%20which%20are%20electrical%20components%20of%20the%20computer%20chips%20that%20power%20artificial%20intelligence%20servers%20and%20smartphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744602120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fhp4tfj1g_china-export-downfall_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-halts-export-of-rare-minerals-magnet-as-trade-war-with-us-intensifies-8158767%22%2C%22summary%22%3