p%3EIt%20allows%20moisture%20to%20escape%2C%20preventing%20dampness%20and%20mould%20from%20settling%20in%2C%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20lime%20is%20environmentally%20friendly%2C%20requiring%20less%20energy%20to%20produce%20and%20absorbing%20carbon%20dioxide%20during%20its%20life%20cycle%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinoth%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Reasoning%20how%20historical%20buildings%20constructed%20with%20lime%20mortar%20have%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20thus%20proving%20their%20durability%20%E2%80%94%20Vinoth%20says%20this%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299507%2Feco-friendly-mud-red-stone-kerala-home-skylights-elliptical-windows-save-on-electric-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematerial%E2%80%99s%20resistance%20to%20weather%20and%20erosion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%2C%20the%20carbonation%20process%20involved%20in%20the%20solidification%20of%20the%20lime%20helps%20sequester%20carbon%20and%20reduce%20climate%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20lime%20is%20versatile%20to%20work%20with%2C%20Vinoth%20says%20architects%20should%20comprehend%20its%20types%2C%20properties%2C%20and%20appropriate%20applications.%20%E2%80%9CMaterial%20sourcing%2C%20quality%20assurance%2C%20and%20the%20development%20of%20skilled%20labour%20are%20paramount.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20design%20considerations%20should%20prioritise%20breathability%2C%20ventilation%2C%20and%20long-term%20maintenance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Moss%20walls%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20ever%20thought%20about%20moss%20as%20a%20building%20material%3F%20Architects%20Mitu%20Mathur%20and%20Shriya%20Diwan%20of%C2%A0%20GPM%20Architects%20and%20Planners%20heroed%20it%20in%20one%20of%20their%20projects%2C%20in%20line%20with%20their%20vision%20for%20a%20more%20organic%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20architects%20say%20the%20material%20combines%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352270%2Fsustainable-home-in-maharashtra-naturally-cool-summers-mango-trees-shriya-parasrampuria-prashant-dupare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20maintenance%20and%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bringing%20a%20biophilic%20touch%20to%20interiors.%20The%20%E2%80%98walls%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20add%2C%20require%20no%20watering%20or%20sunlight.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20customisable%20and%20eco-friendly%2C%20offering%20functional%20and%20aesthetic%20benefits%20ideal%20for%20modern%20interior%20spaces.%E2%80%9D%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20boons%20is%20their%20acoustic%20properties.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMitu%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CMoss%20walls%20absorb%20sound%20and%20reduce%20noise%20reverberation%2C%20creating%20quieter%20and%20more%20comfortable%20indoor%20environments.%20They%20are%20particularly%20effective%20in%20open-plan%20offices%20where%20sound%20control%20is%20a%20priority.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Moss%20walls%20require%20little%20maintenance%20and%20upkeep%20and%20act%20as%20great%20air%20purifiers%20to%20filter%20out%20volatile%20organic%20compounds%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-1744381698-