%20on%20some%20of%20them.%20The%20statement%20came%20after%20a%20bruising%20week%20that%20shook%20investor%20faith%20in%20the%20world's%20reserve%20currency%20as%20Trump's%20tariff%20plans%20whipsawed%20global%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20American%20leader%20pushed%20back%20against%20suggestions%20that%20Friday's%20pausing%20of%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20on%20several%20countries%20was%20letting%20them%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20hook%26quot%3B%20for%20levies%20on%20US%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNOBODY%20is%20getting%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20hook%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20unfair%20Trade%20Balances%2C%20and%20Non%20Monetary%20Tariff%20Barriers%2C%20that%20other%20Countries%20have%20used%20against%20us%2C%20especially%20not%20China%20which%2C%20by%20far%2C%20treats%20us%20the%20worst!%20There%20was%20no%20Tariff%20%26quot%3Bexception%26quot%3B%20announced%20on%20Friday%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wroteon%20his%20Social%20truth%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20explained%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20products%20are%20subject%20to%20the%20existing%2020%20per%20cent%20Fentanyl%20Tariffs%2C%20and%20they%20are%20just%20moving%20to%20a%20different%20Tariff%20bucket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F114332337028519855%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Fake%20News%20knows%20this%2C%20but%20refuses%20to%20report%20it.%20We%20are%20taking%20a%20look%20at%20Semiconductors%20and%20the%20WHOLE%20ELECTRONICS%20SUPPLY%20CHAIN%20in%20the%20upcoming%20National%20Security%20Tariff%20Investigations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20wrote%2C%20referring%20to%20media%20reports%20suggesting%20exemptions%20for%20electronics%20like%20smartphones%20and%20semiconductors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20has%20long%20accused%20Chinese%20corporations%20of%20knowingly%20supplying%20groups%20involved%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20synthetic%20opioid%2C%20which%20sparked%20a%20drug%20crisis%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20further%20reasserted%20his%20intention%20to%20bring%20manufacturing%20back%20to%20America.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20has%20been%20exposed%20is%20that%20we%20need%20to%20make%20products%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20that%20we%20will%20not%20be%20held%20hostage%20by%20other%20Countries%2C%20especially%20hostile%20trading%20Nations%20like%20China%2C%20which%20will%20do%20everything%20within%20its%20power%20to%20disrespect%20the%20American%20People.%20We%20also%20cannot%20let%20them%20continue%20to%20abuse%20us%20on%20Trade%2C%20like%20they%20have%20for%20decades%2C%20THOSE%20DAYS%20ARE%20OVER%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20elaborating%20on%20his%20MAGA%20(Make%20America%20Great%20Again)%20plans%2C%20the%20Republican%20billionaire%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Golden%20Age%20of%20America%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20upcoming%20Tax%20and%20Regulation%20Cuts%2C%20a%20substantial%20amount%20of%20which%20was%20just%20approved%20by%20the%20House%20and%20Senate%2C%20will%20mean%20more%20and%20better%20paying%20Jobs%2C%20making%20products%20in%20our%20Nation%2C%20and%20treating%20other%20Countries%2C%20in%20particular%20China%2C%20the%20same%20way%20they%20have%20treated%20us.%20The%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20our%20Country%20will%20be%20bigger%2C%20better%2C%20and%20stronger%20than%20ever%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20leader's%20statement%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20United%20States%20published%20guidance%2C%20saying%20smartphones%2C%20computers%20and%20other%20electronics%20were%20exempted%20from%20the%20'reciprocal%20tariffs'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20Taiffs%20Coming%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20US%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20move%20to%20exempt%20a%20range%20of%20electronic%20devices%20from%20tariffs%20was%20only%20a%20temporary%20reprieve%2C%20and%20announced%20that%20those%20items%20would%20be%20subject%20to%20%26quot%3Bsemiconductor%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20likely%20come%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20month%20or%20two.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20those%20products%20are%20going%20to%20come%20under%20semiconductors%2C%20and%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20special%20focus%20type%20of%20tariff%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20those%20products%20get%20reshored.%20We%20need%20to%20have%20semiconductors%2C%20we%20need%20to%20have%20chips%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20have%20flat%20panels%20--%20we%20need%20to%20have%20these%20things%20made%20in%20America.%20We%20can't%20be%20reliant%20on%20Southeast%20Asia%20for%20all%20of%20the%20things%20that%20operate%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Lutnick%20told%20%26quot%3BThis%20Week%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20what%20%5BPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%5D%20doing%20is%20he's%20saying%20they're%20exempt%20from%20the%20reciprocal%20tariffs%2C%20but%20they're%20included%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20tariffs%2C%20which%20are%20coming%20in%20probably%20a%20month%20or%20two.%20So%20these%20are%20coming%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744596840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fa6q7q4hs_donald-trump-afp_625x300_12_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-suggests-further-chinese-tariffs-nobody-getting-off-the-hook-8158508%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20hardline%20trade%20policies%2C%20saying%20that%20no%20country%20-%20especially%20China%20-%20would%20be%20getting%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20hook%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20his%20sweeping%20tariffs%2C%20ev