w%20You%26quot%3B%3A%20Netanyahu's%20Son%20Slams%20Macron's%20Plan%20To%20Recognise%20Palestine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20on%20Sunday%20lashed%20out%20at%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20over%20his%20plans%20to%20recognise%20a%20Palestinian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Macron%20is%20gravely%20mistaken%20in%20continuing%20to%20promote%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20our%20land%20--%20a%20state%20whose%20sole%20aspiration%20is%20the%20destruction%20of%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20addressing%20Macron's%20remarks%20earlier%20this%20week%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20France%20could%20recognise%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20within%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20this%20day%2C%20not%20a%20single%20figure%20in%20Hamas%20or%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20has%20condemned%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20worst%20massacre%20of%20Jews%20since%20the%20Holocaust%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20October%207%2C%202023%20attack%20led%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20this%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20silence%20that%20reveals%20their%20true%20attitude%20toward%20the%20Jewish%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20endanger%20our%20existence%20over%20illusions%20detached%20from%20reality%2C%20and%20we%20will%20not%20accept%20moral%20lectures%20about%20establishing%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20that%20would%20threaten%20Israel's%20survival%20--%20especially%20not%20from%20those%20who%20oppose%20granting%20independence%20to%20Corsica%2C%20New%20Caledonia%2C%20French%20Guiana%2C%20and%20other%20territories%2C%20whose%20independence%20would%20pose%20no%20threat%20to%20France%20whatsoever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20echoed%20those%20of%20his%20son%20Yair%2C%20who%20struck%20out%20at%20Macron%20in%20an%20earlier%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScrew%20you!%26quot%3B%20Yair%20Netanyahu%20wrote%20in%20English%20late%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%20to%20independence%20of%20New%20Caledonia!%20Yes%20to%20independence%20to%20French%20Polynesia!%20Yes%20to%20independence%20of%20Corsica!%20Yes%20to%20independence%20of%20the%20Basque%20Country!%20Yes%20to%20independence%20of%20French%20Guinea!%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20apparently%20confusing%20it%20with%20French%20Guiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Legitimate%20right'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20France%205%20broadcast%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20stated%20that%20France%20could%20take%20the%20step%20during%20a%20UN%20conference%20in%20New%20York%20in%20June%2C%20saying%20he%20hoped%20this%20would%20trigger%20a%20reciprocal%20recognition%20of%20Israel%20by%20Arab%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20move%20towards%20recognition%2C%20and%20we%20will%20do%20so%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Macron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20do%20it%20because%20I%20believe%20that%20at%20some%20point%20it%20will%20be%20right%20and%20because%20I%20also%20want%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20collective%20dynamic%2C%20which%20must%20also%20allow%20all%20those%20who%20defend%20Palestine%20to%20recognise%20Israel%20in%20turn%2C%20which%20many%20of%20them%20do%20not%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20sparked%20a%20wave%20of%20criticism%20from%20right-wing%20groups%20in%20France%2C%20after%20which%20Macron%20appeared%20to%20clarify%20his%20initial%20remarks%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20support%20the%20legitimate%20right%20of%20Palestinians%20to%20a%20state%20and%20to%20peace%2C%20just%20as%20I%20support%20the%20right%20of%20Israelis%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20and%20security%2C%20both%20recognised%20by%20their%20neighbours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20doing%20everything%20I%20can%20with%20our%20partners%20to%20reach%20this%20goal%20of%20peace.%20We%20truly%20need%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20Israel%20and%20France%20have%20deteriorated%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%20has%20long%20championed%20a%20two-state%20solution%20to%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict%2C%20including%20after%20the%20October%207%2C%202023%20attack%20by%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20formal%20recognition%20by%20Paris%20of%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20would%20mark%20a%20major%20policy%20switch%20and%20risk%20antagonising%20Israel%2C%20which%20insists%20such%20moves%20by%20foreign%20states%20are%20premature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%20would%20be%20the%20most%20significant%20European%20power%20to%20recognise%20a%20Palestinian%20state%2C%20a%20move%20the%20United%20States%20has%20also%20long%20resisted.%20Hamas%20welcomed%20Macron's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20150%20countries%20recognise%20a%20Palestinian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20May%2C%20Ireland%2C%20Norway%20and%20Spain%20announced%20recognition%2C%20followed%20by%20Slovenia%20in%20June%2C%20moves%20partly%20fuelled%20by%20condemnation%20of%20Israel's%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20that%20followed%20the%20October%207%2C%202023%20Hamas%20attacks%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744594620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fej4i7528_yair-macron_625x300_14_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnetanyahus-son-yair-netanyahu-slams-french-president-emmanuel-macrons-plan-to-recognise-palestine-screw-you-8158410%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20this%20week%20that%20F