iffs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20has%20proven%20that%2C%20for%20example%2C%20when%20he%20threatened%20Mexico%20with%20tariffs%20if%20they%20wouldn't%20cooperate%20with%20'Remain%20in%20Mexico.'%20That%20helped%20secure%20the%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20there's%20certainly%20a%20use%20for%20it%2C%20but%20tariffs%20are%20a%20double-edged%20sword%20and%20a%20pretty%20blunt%20instrument%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20said%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20use%20tariffs%20to%20boost%20federal%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20raise%20revenue%20by%20growing%20your%20economy%2C%20having%20a%20simplified%20and%20rational%20tax%20system%20that%20incentivizes%20economic%20growth%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20slapping%20on%20higher%20tax%20rates%20or%20engaging%20in%20a%20massive%20trade%20war%20that%20obviously%20has%20disrupted%20and%20scared%20the%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-ron-johnson-trade-strategy-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744580070000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fc2a87a466d2b74ab30c64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-ron-johnson-trade-strategy-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20rapid%20tariff%20rate%20changes%20have%20led%20to%20volatility%20in%20both%20the%20stock%20and%20bond%20markets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A391%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-ron-johnson-trade-strategy-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Gravely%20mistaken'%3A%20Netanyahu%20slams%20Macron's%20recognition%20plan%20for%20Palestinian%20state%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe