0test%20%E2%80%94%20began%20waning%20around%202019%2C%20and%20its%20effort%20to%20provide%20more%20consumer%20value%20through%20additional%20services%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20close%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20October%202023%2C%20hackers%20accessed%20the%20personal%20details%20of%20some%20users%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F23andme-data-stolen-hacked-sold-dark-web-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20breach%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20cost%20the%20company%20%2430%20million%20in%20a%20later%20settlement%20agreement.%20The%20breach%20also%20made%20potential%20new%20customers%20nervous%20about%20the%20security%20of%20their%20data%20and%20more%20resistant%20to%20purchasing%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20announcement%20that%20it%20was%20filing%20for%20bankruptcy%20and%20seeking%20buyers%20has%20now%20further%20raised%20concerns%20among%20consumers%20about%20the%20security%20of%2023andMe's%20database%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20consumer%20DNA%20databases%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECybersecurity%20experts%20have%20urged%20users%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-delete-your-23andme-data%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20delete%20their%20data%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20pointing%20to%20a%20host%20of%20risks%3A%20Genetic%20data%20can%20be%20used%20to%20further%20discrimination%2C%20enable%20financial%20fraud%2C%20and%20develop%20biological%20weapons%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E23andMe%20has%20said%20it%20will%20continue%20operating%20until%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2F23andme-confirms-all-potential-buyers-must-agree-to-comply-with-privacy-policy-and-applicable-law-1034518487%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuyer%20is%20found%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20race%20to%20acquire%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20data%20%E2%80%94%20has%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20sale%20and%20what%20might%20happen%20to%20your%20DNA%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223535d598-d680-49cb-ad57-efd60bb1af9b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20genetic%20data%20does%2023andMe%20even%20collect%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E23andMe%20gathers%20genetic%20data%20using%20saliva%20samples.%20Consumers%20receive%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-the-new-23andme-genetic-test-2015-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollection%20kit%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20submit%20about%202%20milliliters%20of%20saliva.%20Each%20kit%20has%20a%20collection%20tube%20labeled%20with%20a%2014-digit%20barcode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20sample%20passes%20visual%20inspection%2C%20the%20barcode%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20the%20only%20identifying%20information%20shared%20with%20the%20laboratory%20%E2%80%94%20is%20scanned%20and%20the%20sample%20moves%20to%20DNA%20extraction%2C%26quot%3B%2023andMe%20spokesperson%20Ann%20Sommerlath%20told%20BI%20by%20email.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20a%20sample%20is%20successfully%20genotyped%2C%20the%20laboratory%20sends%20the%20resulting%20data%20back%20to%2023andMe%20along%20with%20the%20accompanying%20barcode%2C%20at%20which%20point%20we%20can%20begin%20interpreting%20your%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenotyping%20is%20the%20process%20identifying%20variations%20in%20someone's%20genetic%20code.%20These%20variations%20influence%20a%20person's%20physical%20traits%2C%20their%20development%2C%20and%20susceptibility%20to%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ebd6e2c4-b2f7-44ca-8ba1-6d7c548bb36e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20the%20company%20handle%20its%20genetic%20data%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20sharing%20individual%20genetic%20reports%20with%20customers%2C%20if%20they%20opt-in%2C%2023andMe%20says%20it%20uses%20anonymized%20genetic%20and%20self-reported%20information%20for%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20customers%20agree%20to%20participate%20in%2023andMe%20Research%20via%20our%20consent%20document%2C%20they%20give%2023andMe%20permission%20to%20share%20their%20de-identified%2C%20individual-level%20data%20with%20approved%2C%20qualified%20research%20collaborators%20outside%20of%2023andMe%2C%26quot%3B%20Sommerlath%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BDe-identification%20(replacing%20personal%20information%20with%20a%20random%20ID)%20enables%20researchers%20to%20protect%20the%20identity%20of%20individuals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E23andMe%20shares%20some%20of%20the%20resulting%20research%20in%20its%20blog.%20In%20a%20piece%20from%20November%202024%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20company%20wrote%20that%20many%20of%20its%20users%20are%20descendants%20of%20Mayflower%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E23andMe%20was%20found%20to%20offer%20the%20%26quot%3Bclearest%20privacy%20policy%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20review%20of%2010%20popular%20genetic%20testing%20services%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Ancestry%2C%20Toolbox%20Genomics%2C%20and%20Everlywell%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20conducted%20by%20the%20data%20privacy%20service%20Icogni.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5290802-c114-44ed-9684-df6a0e8865dc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20a%2023andMe%20buyer%20have%20to%20comply%20with%20its%20privacy%20policy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20And%20then%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20make%20a%20qualified%20bid%2C%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20buyers%20must%2C%20among%20other%20requirements%2C%20agree%20to%20comply%20with%2023andMe's%20consumer%20privacy%20policy%20and%20all%20applicable%20laws%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20treatment%20of%20customer%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20posted%20to%20its%20website%20on%20March%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERon%20Zayas%2C%20CEO%20of%20Ironwall%2C%20a%20privacy%20service%20offered%20by%20Incogni%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20letter%20is%20just%20a%20guideline%20and%20leaves%20several%20questions%20unanswered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20how%20long%20is%20the%20letter%20good%20for%3F%20A%20day%20after%20purchase%2C%20a%20year%3F%26quot%3B%20Zayas%20asked.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20a%20company%20like%20a%20data%20broker%20buys%20the%20company%3F%20It%20may%20change%20the%20definition%20of%20all%20the%20terms%20in%20the%20letter%20and%20even%20the%20privacy%20statement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Farrow%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Anderson%2C%20Williams%2C%20%26amp%3B%20Farrow%2C%20said%20the%20new%20owner%20isn't%20legally%20bound%20to%20the%20existing%20privacy%20policy%20after%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20way%20a%20court%20will%20say%20the%20terms%20of%20service%20can%20never%20be%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20buying%20a%20car.%20Once%20you%20own%20it%2C%20you%20can%20paint%20it%2C%20change%20the%20interior%2C%20do%20anything%20you%20want%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThorin%20Klosowski%2C%20a%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprivacy%20and%20security%20activist%20at%20the%20Electronic%20Frontier%20Foundation%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20the%20security%20of%20a%20user's%2023andMe%20data%20will%20depend%20on%20who%20purchases%20the%20biotech%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20take%20very%20many%20leaps%20of%20logic%20to%20think%20through%20some%20of%20the%20worst-case%20scenarios%2C%26quot%3B%20Klosowski%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20that%20is%20an%20insurance%20company%20or%20a%20company%20that%20would%20grant%20easier%20access%20for%20law%20enforcement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20bid%20requirements%20for%2023andMe%2C%20Klosowski%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20really%20know%20how%20that's%20going%20to%20play%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20an%20unscrupulous%20company%20didn't%20do%20that.%20We%20don't%20know%20how%20closely%20they%20would%20be%20monitored%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209083b40-7552-4f27-91f2-8de56cb9e4e9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20wants%20to%20buy%20the%20company%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWojcicki%2C%20for%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20resigned%20as%20CEO%20of%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bso%20I%20can%20be%20in%20the%20best%20position%20to%20pursue%20the%20company%20as%20an%20independent%20bidder%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20March%2024%20announcing%20the%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20handful%20of%20other%20companies%20have%20also%20expressed%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENucleus%20Genomics%2C%20founded%20by%2025-year-old%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20dropout%20Kian%20Sadeghi%2C%20has%20explored%20the%20possibility%20of%20purchasing%2023andMe.%20For%20Nucleus%20Genomics%20%E2%80%94%20a%20new%20player%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuture-healthcare-dna-genetic-testing-23andme-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenetic%20testing%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20focused%20on%20whole%20genome%20testing%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20some%20value%20in%20the%20data%20and%20technology%20of%20a%20company%20with%20a%2020-year%20history%2C%20Sadeghi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto%20nonprofit%20Sei%20Foundation%20has%20also%20expressed%20interest%20in%20acquiring%2023andMe.%20%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20just%20another%20bankruptcy.%20It's%20a%20digital%20land%20grab%20on%20one%20of%20history's%20most%20profoundly%20intimate%20data%20sets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Sei%20Foundation%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20March%2031.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20invested%20long-term%20in%20returning%20intellectual%20property%20(including%20your%20DNA)%20to%20the%20people.%20It's%20the%20American%20thing%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPinnacle%2C%20an%20analytics%20company%2C%20is%20also%20apparently%20interested.%20In%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20addressed%20to%2023andMe's%20shareholders%2C%20Pinnacle%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Ryan%20Sitton%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20give%20you%20%24100%20million%20for%2023andMe%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbf0b5b5-81c0-446f-8677-df9d68e55c65%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20valuable%20is%20its%20genetic%20data%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20formula%20for%20quantifying%20the%20value%20of%2023andMe's%20data%2C%20so%20potential%20buyers%20and%20informed%20speculators%20are%20making%20educated%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKanyi%20Maqubela%2C%20managing%20partner%20of%20venture%20capital%20firm%20Kindred%20Ventures%2C%20which%20has%20invested%20in%20several%20healthcare%20companies%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20genetic%20data%20is%20particularly%20valuable%20for%20pharmaceutical%20research%20and%20development%20because%20it%20often%20includes%20early%20disease%20markers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPharmaceutical%20companies%20are%20typically%20%26quot%3Bvery%20data%20hungry%2C%20always%20looking%20for%20new%20data%20pipelines%2C%20and%20always%20looking%20to%20collect%20it%20at%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20So%2C%20%26quot%3Beven%20partial%20genomic%20sequencing%20at%20the%20individual%20level%20is%20quite%20valuable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20even%20more%20valuable%20%26quot%3Bif%20you've%20got%20metadata%20attached%20to%20it%2C%20so%20like%20demographic%20information%2C%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20By%20connecting%20people%20across%20geographies%20and%20disease%20levels%2C%20health%20companies%20can%20start%20drawing%20correlations%20across%20the%20data%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20all%20the%20more%20valuable%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncogni's%20Zayas%20said%20that%2023andMe's%20data%20%26quot%3Bis%20probably%20worth%20more%20than%20the%20service%20they%20were%20selling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20value%20of%20monetized%20information%2C%20a%20good%20cellphone%20can%20go%20for%20%2450%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BGood%20buyer%20information%2C%20good%20credit%20card%20information%2C%20good%20demographic%20information%2C%20you%20can%20start%20looking%20at%20tens%20or%20even%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20per%20individual.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E23andMe%20has%20access%20to%20all%20of%20that%20and%20more%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BJust%20in%20research%20for%20insurance%20companies%2C%20that's%20got%20to%20be%20worth%20at%20least%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20per%20individual.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20says%20it%20has%20over%2015%20million%20customers%2C%20so%20by%20Zayas'%20calculations%20the%20data%20itself%20is%20worth%20several%20billions%2C%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJessica%20Vitak%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland's%20College%20of%20Information%20who%20researches%20data%20privacy%2C%20told%20BI%20that%2023andMe's%20data%20is%20%26quot%3Bfairly%20unique%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20revealing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20tremendous%20trove%20of%20not%20just%20genetic%20data%20tied%20to%20those%20accounts%2C%20but%20the%20majority%20of%20people%20who%20use%20the%20service%20also%20completed%20surveys%2C%20so%20there%20are%20other%20data%20points%20that%20would%20interest%20various%20third%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20Vitak%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20advertisers%2C%20health%20researchers%2C%20or%20people%20selling%20data%20to%20a%20whole%20range%20of%20entities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVitak%20said%20the%20depth%20of%20information%20is%20one%20reason%2023andMe's%20data%20is%20so%20valuable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20thing%20if%20I%20decide%20to%20share%20information%20about%20myself%2C%20but%20genetic%20data%20isn't%20just%20about%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Vitak%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20all%20my%20direct%20family%20members%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESadeghi%20from%20Nucleus%20Genomics%2C%20however%2C%20said%20he%20is%20not%20making%20a%20bid%20because%20he%20thinks%20the%20data%20is%20valuable%20but%20instead%20because%20of%20another%20company%2023andMe%20acquired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E23andMe%20only%20gathers%20%26quot%3Ba%20small%20sliver%20of%20someone's%20DNA%20and%20the%20most%20critical%20genetic%20markers%20are%20actually%20completely%20absent%20from%20the%20data.%20They're%20just%20not%20there%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20it%20actually%20doesn't%20work%20for%20drug%20discovery.%20That's%20why%20it%20never%20worked%20as%20a%20clinical%20test%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20data%20is%20worth%20something%2C%20but%20is%20it%20worth%20anywhere%20near%20what%20people%20are%20positing%20today%3F%20Absolutely%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESadeghi%20said%20the%20real%20value%20of%2023andMe%20is%20in%20Lemonaid%20Health%20%E2%80%94%20the%20telehealth%20company%20it%20acquired%20for%20%24400%20million%20in%202021%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20way%20to%20connect%20with%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a08dbcd-9f93-42a4-b46d-436f29e6d2e1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20the%20new%20owners%20do%20with%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20genetic%20data%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESadeghi%20said%20he%20sees%20the%20data%20as%20one%20component%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Breal-time%2C%20consumer-centric%2C%20quantified%20health%20platform%26quot%3B%20he%20wants%20to%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20reason%20why%20you%20can't%20bring%20together%20someone's%20blood%2C%20genetics%2C%20drugs%2C%20urinary%20analysis%2C%20full%20body%20MRIs%2C%20wearables%2C%20all%20together%20in%20a%20single%20platform%20that%20can%20basically%20completely%20revolutionize%20disease%20prevention%2C%20disease%20diagnosis%2C%20and%20also%20disease%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKindred's%20Maqubela%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20roots%20for%20a%20bankruptcy%2C%26quot%3B%20but%2023andMe's%20data%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Btreasure%20trove%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20thinks%20could%20help%20grow%20the%20burgeoning%20field%20of%20multi-omics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMulti-omics%20combines%20data%20from%20the%20genome%20(genes)%2C%20proteome%20(proteins)%2C%20transcriptome%20(RNA%20transcripts)%2C%20epigenome%20(modifications%20to%20DNA)%2C%20metabolome%20(molecules%20produced%20in%20metabolism)%2C%20microbiome%20(fungi%2C%20bacteria%2C%20viruses)%2C%20and%20more%20to%20create%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20picture%20of%20human%20biology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20young%20field%2C%20mostly%20stuck%20right%20now%20in%20pharma%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20and%20then%20in%20some%20bench%20and%20lab%20research%2C%20and%20so%20it%20hasn't%20yet%20broken%20into%20scaled%20provider%20and%20end%20patient%20uses%2C%20but%20it's%20going%20to%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%2023andMe's%20data%2C%20he%20added%2C%20could%20accelerate%20the%20development%20of%20mult-omics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaqubela%20said%20the%20recent%20advances%20in%20AI%20also%20present%20new%20opportunities%20to%20use%20this%20data.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20put%20it%20in%20pre-training%20for%20a%20big%20LLM%2C%20what%20comes%20out%20on%20the%20other%20end%20of%20that%20is%20actually%20very%20hard%20to%20know%20and%20could%20be%20very%2C%20very%2C%20very%20interesting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20large%20language%20models%20like%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVitak%20said%20potential%20buyers%20could%20use%20the%20data%20for%20research.%20%26quot%3B23andMe%20partnered%20with%20numerous%20researchers%2C%20so%20there%20could%20be%20buyers%20that%20would%20continue%20to%20expand%20access%20to%20that%20type%20of%20data%20to%20advance%20precision%20medicine%20or%20other%20types%20of%20research%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20breadth%2C%20nature%2C%20and%20potential%20of%2023andMe's%20data%2C%20Vitak%20and%20Klosowski%20said%20the%20sale%20is%20unprecedented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20organization%20dealing%20with%20data%20as%20sensitive%20as%20our%20genetic%20material%20has%20a%20moral%20responsibility%20to%20take%20extra%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20Vitak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc643e0d-3128-420a-aa0e-1bc0038629bc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20laws%20that%20exist%20to%20protect%20you%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVitak%20and%20Klosowski%20said%20consumers%20need%20more%20federal%20protections%20regarding%20genetic%20data%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20states%20have%20implemented%20laws%20to%20help%20protect%20consumer%20data%2C%20including%20Montana%2C%20where%2C%20in%202023%2C%20state%20legislators%20passed%20the%20Genetic%20Information%20Privacy%20Act%2C%20which%20is%20focused%20on%20protecting%20consumers'%20genetic%20data.%20California%20has%20similar%20protections%20for%20genetic%20data%20with%20direct-to-consumer%20testing%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20enforces%20the%20Genetic%20Information%20Nondiscrimination%20Act%2C%20which%20bars%20employers%20and%20health%20insurers%20from%20discriminating%20against%20individuals%20based%20on%20genetic%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Vitak%20said%20the%20United%20States%20also%20needs%20something%20like%20the%20EU's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-gdpr-regulation-explained-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Data%20Protection%20Regulation%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20enforces%20broader%20protections%20for%20data%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20data%20breach%20and%20the%20sale%20are%20further%20making%20the%20case%20for%20why%20we%20need%20stronger%20data%20protection%20for%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20Vitak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F23andme-what-happens-to-genetic-data-buyers-sale-bankruptcy-security-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744565204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f98892c6ad288d147e027e%3Fformat%