ustainable%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Younis%20Malik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20creating%20strong%20backward%20and%20forward%20linkages%2C%20we%20have%20ensured%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20smooth%20operation%20and%20scalability%2C%20which%20not%20only%20addresses%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418606%2Fmanoj-mahajan-ias-initiative-for-waste-management-in-rural-sundargarh-odisha-empower-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Dal%20Lake%20but%20also%20offers%20a%20replicable%20model%20for%20other%20lake%20conservation%20projects.%20The%20initiative%20has%20had%20a%20positive%20environmental%20impact%20by%20converting%20lake%20biomass%20into%20bio-manure%2C%20contributing%20to%20both%20conservation%20efforts%20and%20agricultural%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGreener%20lakes%2C%20stronger%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20environmental%20impact%2C%20CEF%20Group%20has%20made%20strides%20in%20managing%20the%20excess%20lake%20weed.%20Between%20August%20and%20December%202024%2C%20they%20received%20a%20total%20of%2014%2C864%20tonnes%20of%20lake%20weed.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%204%2C131%20tonnes%20were%20converted%20into%20organic%20manure%2C%20a%20process%20that%20has%20led%20to%20a%20reduction%20of%20approximately%202%2C891%20tonnes%20of%20CO%E2%82%82%20emissions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20perspective%2C%20converting%20just%20one%20tonne%20of%20lake%20weed%20into%20organic%20manure%20results%20in%20a%20CO2%20savings%20of%20around%200.7%20tonnes.%20%E2%80%9COur%20project%20is%20designed%20to%20process%20up%20to%2070%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20lake%20weed%20each%20year%2C%20which%20yields%20between%2020%2C000%20to%2022%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20manure.%20This%20large-scale%20effort%20is%20expected%20to%20lead%20to%20an%20annual%20reduction%20of%20around%2050%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20CO%E2%82%82%20emissions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Maninder%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20important%20aspect%20of%20this%20process%20is%20the%20leachate%20treatment%2C%20which%20involves%20the%20water%20that%20is%20extracted%20from%20the%20lake%20weeds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20lake%20weeds%20is%20carefully%20treated%20to%20remove%20any%20harmful%20contaminants%20like%20heavy%20metals%2C%20organic%20pollutants%2C%20and%20other%20toxic%20substances%2C%20through%20our%20leachate%20treatment%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20treated%2C%20this%20water%20is%20safely%20returned%20to%20the%20soil%2C%20ensuring%20that%20it%20nourishes%20the%20land%20without%20causing%20any%20negative%20environmental%20impact.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comprehensive%20approach%20not%20only%20helps%20manage%20the%20invasive%20lake%20weed%20problem%20but%20also%20contributes%20to%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices%20by%20providing%20nutrient-rich%20organic%20manure%20while%20reducing%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20improving%20the%20health%20of%20the%20surrounding%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20the%20farmers%20of%20Kashmir%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20conversion%20has%20also%20benefitted%20around%202%2C500%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20so%20far%2C%20who%20now%20have%20access%20to%20organic%20manure%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20%E2%80%94%20Rs%2012%20per%20kg%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20Rs%2016%20per%20kg%20they%20were%20paying%20for%20chemical%20fertilisers%20brought%20in%20from%20other%20states%20like%20UP%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%20an%20impact%20by%20enriching%20over%204%2C400%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20improving%20soil%20health%2C%20and%20supporting%20sustainable%20agriculture%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfi