foundation-plantation-7-1744205181.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20steps%20of%20rewilding%20barren%20areas%20of%20land%20across%20India%20involve%20firstly%20narrowing%20down%20on%20areas%20which%20have%20been%20ridden%20by%20mining%20and%20de-forestation%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-7-1744205181-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20steps%20of%20rewilding%20barren%20areas%20of%20land%20across%20India%20involve%20narrowing%20down%20areas%20which%20have%20been%20ridden%20by%20mining%20and%20deforestation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20inspection%20of%20the%20land%2C%20a%20land%20letter%20is%20acquired%20from%20the%20government.%20This%20documentation%20legally%20allows%20CATCH%20Foundation%20to%20lease%20the%20land%20and%20subject%20it%20to%20reforestation%20efforts.%20The%20next%20step%20is%20soil%20testing%20(and%20conducting%20a%20baseline%20survey%20of%20the%20site%20before%20plantation)%2C%20borewell%20digging%2C%20and%20then%20the%20creation%20of%20fencing%20systems%20to%20prevent%20any%20intervention%20from%20the%20local%20groups%20of%20domestic%20animals%20that%20might%20harm%20the%20plantation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CATCH%20team%20works%20on%20the%20project%20with%20post-plantation%20maintenance.%20They%20share%20that%20the%20team%20employs%20and%20trains%20local%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20ensures%20regular%20activities%20and%20ensures%20the%20forest%20is%20made%20self-sustainable%20in%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FByvdpRw4nMA%3Fsi%3DGdOmGtAyfjsgXeM6%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20integrating%20solar%20systems%20(in%20some%20cases)%20to%20harness%20green%20power%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20make%20the%20forest%20grid-free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20is%20the%20excavation%20stage%20where%20the%20land%20is%20prepared%20for%20plantation.%20Its%20productivity%20is%20enhanced%20with%20cow%20dung%20and%20rice%20husks%3B%20the%20latter%20is%20a%20dense%20source%20of%20carbon%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20water%20and%20nutrient-holding%20capacity%20of%20the%20soil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soil%20is%20mulched%20with%20agro-waste%20and%20then%20nourished%20with%20manure%20and%20vermicompost%2C%20which%20boost%20its%20nutrition%20quotient.%20What%20follows%20is%20the%20plantation%20activity.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20forest%20created%20by%20CATCH%20Foundation%20is%20a%20green%20oasis%20around%20which%20civilisation%20thrives.%20The%20foundation%20wishes%20to%20make%20forests%20mainstays%20in%20cities%20rather%20than%20fleeting%20inclusions.%20To%20ensure%20this%20permanence%2C%20there%20is%20a%20stringent%20assessment%20of%20these%20forests%20during%20the%20first%20three%20years.%20One%20of%20the%20main%20aims%20during%20this%20time%20is%20to%20keep%20the%20forest%20weed-free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Catch%20Foundation%20does%20a%20routine%20maintenance%20of%20the%20forest%20for%20three%20years%20after%20which%20the%20forest%20is%20considered%20mature%20enough%20to%20thrive%20by%20itself%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418905%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECatch%20Foundation%20does%20routine%20maintenance%20of%20the%20forest%20for%20three%20years%2C%20after%20which%20the%20forest%20is%20considered%20mature%20enough%20to%20thrive%20by%20itself%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20forest%20is%20thriving%20without%20intervention%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20plenty.%20The%20most%20important%20of%20these%20is%20carbon%20sequestration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20mature%20tree%20can%20absorb%20around%2048%20pounds%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20per%20year.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20trees%20lower%20the%20ambient%20temperatures%2C%20creating%20a%20more%20comfortable%20microclimate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESparking%20a%20positive%20revolution%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20trees%20absorb%20excess%20water%2C%20these%20forests%20reduce%20surface%20runoff%2C%20thus%20reducing%20the%20risk%20of%20flooding%20in%20heavy%20rainfall%20events.%20This%20success%20is%20mirrored%20by%20the%20project%20at%20Vadodara%2C%20where%20L%26amp%3BT%20partnered%20with%20CATCH%20Foundation%20to%20create%20multiple%20forests%20with%2050%2C000%20trees%20in%20the%20Harni%20area%20of%20Vadodara.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%20Shah%2C%20who%20leads%20CSR%20initiatives%20in%20the%20Vadodara%20region%20for%20L%26amp%3BT%20Energy%20Hydrocarbon%2C%20is%20fascinated%20by%20how%20tech-driven%20monitoring%20tools%20enabled%20them%20to%20track%20the%20health%20and%20growth%20of%20each%20forest%20patch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-10-1744205747.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20barren%20landscapes%20to%20lush%20forests%2C%20CATCH%20Foundation%20is%20bringing%20about%20a%20green%20revolution%20in%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-10-1744205747.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-10-1744205747-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-10-1744205747-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-10-1744205747-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-10-1744205747-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418928%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20barren%20landscapes%20to%20lush%20forests%2C%20CATCH%20Foundation%20is%20bringing%20about%20a%20green%20revolution%20in%20India%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20impact%20is%20visible%2C%20some%20of%20these%20forests%20are%20already%20mature%20and%20self-sustaining%2C%20showing%20remarkable%20progress%20within%20just%20two%20years.%20It%20has%20attracted%20biodiversity%20and%20promoted%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20better%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20forests%20are%20helping%20mitigate%20the%20effects%20of%20urbanisation%20in%20Vadodara.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20always%20the%20challenge%20of%20balancing%20development%20with%20sustainability.%20The%20green%20transformation%20is%20crucial%20because%20it%20addresses%20both%20climate%20and%20community%20needs.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Vadodara%20model%20perfectly%20underscores%20how%20urbanisation%20and%20green%20ecosystems%20can%20thrive%20hand-in-hand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20104%20forests%20created%20across%20India%2C%20CATCH%20Foundation%20is%20reimagining%20our%20cities%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20world%20in%20which%20we%20live.%20CATCH%20partners%20with%20many%20CSR%20collaborators%20in%20the%20alignment%20of%20environmental%20conservation%20and%20the%20goal%20of%20improving%20urban%20greenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%2C%20All%20images%20courtesy%20CATCH%20Foundation%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744206724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation_11zon-1744204203.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D418850%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20a%20sapling%2C%20a%20forest%20can%20spurt.%20CATCH%20Foundation%20has%20been%20putting%20this%20belief%20into%20practice%20since%202014%20as%20they%20use%20reforestation%20to%20transform%20barren%20landscapes%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A394%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418850%2Fcatch-foundation-uses-reforestation-to-transform-barren-lands-in-india-creates-forests%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98She%20Was%20Widowed%20at%2016%2C%20Started%20a%20Pickle%20Biz%20at%2065%E2%80%99%3A%20This%20Daughter%20is%20Carrying%20Forward%20Her%20Amma%E2%80%99s%20Legacy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHidden%20in%20a%20corner%20of%20the%20Internet%E2%80%99s%20archive%20is%20a%20tasty%20secret%20%E2%80%94%20one%20saut%C3%A9ed%20in%20cold-pressed%20oils%2C%20and%20enhanced%20with%3Cem%3E%20sendha%20namak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Himalayan%20pink%20salt).%20A%20secret%20is%20only%20as%20good%20as%20its%20keeper.%20And%20so%2C%20we%20took%20it%20upon%20ourselves%20to%20trace%20Shyamlata%20Sihare%20down%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20two%20continents%2C%20and%20numerous%20cities%2C%20intent%20on%20discovering%20her%20journey%20of%20building%20%E2%80%98Old%20Fashioned%20Gourmet%E2%80%99%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Aravali%20Foods%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F292787%2Fmasterchef-australia-sandeep-pandit-revives-traditional-kashmiri-pandit-recipes-indian-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20secret%20hinged%20on%20traditional%20Indian%20spices%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20time-tested%20cooking%20methods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%E2%80%99s%20pickles%2C%20%3Cem%3Epapads%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fried%20Indian%20snacks)%2C%20squashes%20and%20%3Cem%3Emangodis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(green%20gram%20fritters)%20have%20been%20breathing%20life%20into%20the%20dining%20tables%20of%20India%20since%201993.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20browse%20through%20Old%20Fashioned%20Gourmet%E2%80%99s%20fascinating%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F39